reviewText: Purchased this for my Father-in-law for Father's Day. He is a train enthusiast and just love these dvd's!
fits my collection just fine. thank you
My nephew loves it and cant stop watching it.
came in original package unopened in good shape

I got these for Christmas last year and they are amazing! I drank a bottle of wine and watched 2 hours of trains. Might seem weird to non rail fans but they were some of the best 2 hours of my life. Everything a girl could want!
